## The Analog Kid — Image Definitions

## Click-to-continue bounce indicator
image ctc:
    Text("▼", color="#aaaaaa", size=18)
    block:
        yoffset 0
        linear 0.4 yoffset 7
        linear 0.4 yoffset 0
        repeat
